I'm using my statically typed language and I'm not screwing around with childNodes or getAttribute either (thankfully!):

XElement rss = XElement.Load("http://feeds.feedburner.com/Devhawk");
foreach (XElement item in rss.Element("channel").Elements("item"))
    Console.WriteLine(item.Element("title").Value);

Not quite as elegant as yours, but not too far off. :)
